name: The Hidden Flower
description:
Have you ever take the time to discover the beautiful flower that hides in yourself ? What about the one that hides in others ?

Sometimes the flower hides itself, voluntarily or not, but sometimes it is hidden by another flower. By another...

Offering this flower is sending a message... just like the one I'm trying to send you.

Can you see the flower now ?

(4608x3456)
